                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190113-43-off252 t18190113-43-cd253"></join>, one shirt, value 5 s.; two handkerchiefs, value 4 s., and one pair of stockings, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190113-43-victim460" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Slade
                  <interp inst="t18190113-43-victim460" type="surname" value="Slade"></interp>
